---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="mb-20">
    <p class="font-label text-xs mb-5 tracking-widest" style="color: var(--accent);">
      OPERATIONS & CX LEADER
    </p>
    <h1 class="font-display mb-6" style="font-size: 4rem; line-height: 1.1;">
      <span class="hero-name">Justin M. Hemp</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-base font-label" style="color: var(--muted);">
      MBA · CAPM · Lean Six Sigma Green Belt · LUMA Human-Centered Design
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- About -->
  <section class="mb-16 max-w-2xl">
    <p class="text-lg mb-6" style="color: var(--text); line-height: 1.85;">
      My career has lived at the intersection of operations and people — over a decade at Airbnb
      and Autodesk building and improving the systems that make complex organizations actually work.
      After a deliberate step back to sharpen my toolkit — MBA, CAPM, Lean Six Sigma Green Belt,
      and LUMA Human-Centered Design — I'm focused on what's next: roles in Operations, Program
      Management, CX Strategy, or Business Analysis where I can bring both structure and curiosity
      to real problems.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg" style="color: var(--text); line-height: 1.85;">
      Outside of work, I serve as Board Secretary for Sherwood Charter School, where governance
      and operations overlap in ways I find genuinely energizing. You'll also find me cooking
      something ambitious on a weeknight, traveling when I can, or tinkering with projects like
      the chatbot on this very site.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Quick Facts -->
  <section class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-16">
    {[
      { label: 'BASED IN',   value: 'Portland, OR' },
      { label: 'OPEN TO',    value: 'Ops · PM · CX · BA roles' },
      { label: 'BOARD ROLE', value: 'Sherwood Charter School' },
    ].map(fact => (
      <div style="border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--surface);" class="rounded-lg p-5">
        <p class="font-label text-xs mb-2 tracking-widest" style="color: var(--accent);">{fact.label}</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: var(--text);">{fact.value}</p>
      </div>
    ))}
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="flex gap-3 flex-wrap mb-20">
    <a href="mailto:justin.hemp@gmail.com" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium" style="background-color: var(--accent); color: white;">
      Get in touch →
    </a>
    <a href="/resume" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium" style="border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text);">
      View Resume
    </a>
  </section>
</Layout>